The Templars place a curse on the House of Capet as they are being burned at the stake ("You shall be accursed to the 13th generation!"); Mirri uses blood magic to reduce Khal Drogo to a vegetative state, killing his and Daenerys's unborn child in the process, and prophesies that Drogo will never return to health ("When the sun rises in the west and sets in the east...").
Mirri is burned at the stake by Daenerys as punishment for her betrayal.